ism of the late 1950s, and the post-classical cinema of the turn of the millennium.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aMotion pictureszUnited StatesxHistory. 0aPassing (Identity) in motion pictures. 0aRace in motion pictures. 0aRacism in motion pictures. 4aAmerica. 4aCinema. 4aCultural History. 4aCulture. 4aEthnicity. 4aHollywood. 4aMedia Studies. 4aMedia. 4aRace. 4aRacism. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Media Studies.2bisacsh  aAmerica.  aCinema.  aCultural History.  aCulture.  aEthnicity.  aHollywood.  aMedia Studies.  aMedia.  aRace.  aRacism.1 aEngell, Lorenz, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2z978311074335708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishz978311075400108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021z9783110753776oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Sociology 2021 Englishz978311075418608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Sociology 2021z9783110753967oZDB-23-DSL08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2021z9783111025100oZDB-23-TGP08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript English Frontlist eBook-Package 2021z97831107673150 cprintz978383765337340uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839453377?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839453377423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839453377/original  a978-3-11-074335-7  DG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2b2021  a978-3-11-075400-1  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishb2021  a978-3-11-075418-6  EBOOK PACKAGE Sociology 2021 Englishb2021  a978-3-11-076731-5  transcript Englis